title: Registrasi Employee
steps_actions:
1. Masuk menu PIM
2. Klik tombol Add
3. Input data pada field dan save

* First Name
* Middle name
* Last Name
steps_result:
1. Tampil halaman PIM
2. Redirect page Add employee
3. Berhasil add employee baru
Redirect ke halaman menu PIM
